===Etymology===
From later {{etyl|fro|en}} ''[[coissin]]'' (modern ''[[coussin]]''), ultimately from {{etyl|la|en}} ''[[coxa]]'' via a {{etyl|VL.|en}} root *''coxinum'' ‘hip, thigh’ or alternatively from Latin {{m|la|culcita||mattress}}.

